    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a NameServerSetGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved NameServer Set. A NameServer Set represents a logical entity of the DNSAPI architecture, to link an Account with a NameServer Interface Set, through the configuration of the Name Server names that will be provided to the Account's Zones.
